# Neosys Aeon v4.1 Reform Walkthrough

The platform has been successfully updated to version 4.1, aligning the foundational documentation with the live site and introducing the new 10 Principles of the Cosmos.

## 📄 Whitepaper Updates (v4.1)

All three foundational whitepapers have been updated with the definitive 4.1 text, corrected bibliographic references, and the new 10-principle structure.

- [whitepaper-es.md](file:///Users/yepz/neosysaeon/whitepaper-es.md) (Spanish)
- [whitepaper-en.md](file:///Users/yepz/neosysaeon/whitepaper-en.md) (English)
- [whitepaper-cn.md](file:///Users/yepz/neosysaeon/whitepaper-cn.md) (Chinese)

> [!IMPORTANT]
> The framework has transitioned from a 12-principle structure to a **10-principle structure** focused on "Heurísticas del Sistema".

